{"type":"answer","id":37122,"parentType":"question","parentId":6258,"uid":3487,"contents":"自卖一下，写<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/2881\">政治光谱</a>时，最后谈到中共的定位时，用了Nolan的政治坐标系，比较适合解决题主的矛盾感。在这个坐标系中，共产主义和法西斯主义既不是左，也不是右，而在极权处重合为一体，左右已经失去意义。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qpqv1Nl.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qpqv1Nl.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qpqv1Nl.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-08-13","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}